OL,3,CViolent crimes against women on
OL,4,CBritain's trains jump by more than 50%
OL,6,FNew figures have revealed a sharp rise
OL,7,Fin violence against women and girls on
OL,8,FBritain's railways, Amelia Beckett
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FViolent attacks against women on
OL,12,FBritish railways have more than
OL,13,Fdoubled since 2021, according to new
OL,14,Fdata.
OL,16,FFigures from the British Transport
OL,17,FPolice Authority's 2024 annual report
OL,18,Fshowed the number of crimes against
OL,19,Fwomen and girls rose from 7,561 in
OL,20,F2021 to 11,357 in 2023.
