OL,6,FUnacceptable behaviour such as
OL,7,Fleering, catcalling, touching,
OL,8,Fpressing, upskirting or indecent
OL,9,Fexposure is being experienced by women
OL,10,Fmore than ever, with 51% of female
OL,11,Fvictims stating that other rail
OL,12,Fpassengers intervened to try to help.
OL,14,FHowever, only one in five people who
OL,15,Fhave witnessed incidents of sexual
OL,16,Fharassment reported it to police.
