OL,6,FBTP Detective Chief Superintendent
OL,7,FPaul Furnell last year called on the
OL,8,Fcommunity to watch out and stand up
OL,9,Ffor each other while catching the
OL,10,Ftrain or tube.
OL,12,F"I'll guarantee that most of us have
OL,13,Ftold our daughters, mums, or friends
OL,14,Fto be careful on their way home when
OL,15,Fthey're travelling alone late at night
OL,16,F` perhaps to share their journeys and
OL,17,Fstick to well-lit areas," he said.
